							"host": ["{{SCHEDULER_URL}}"],
							"path": ["tasks", "{{task_id}}", "cancel"]
						},
						"description": "Moves the task to `CANCELLED` and removes it from the scheduler.\n\nOnly allowed from `CREATED` or `PENDING`. Returns `409 Conflict` if the task is already `RUNNING`, `RETRYING`, `SUCCESS`, `FAILED`, or `CANCELLED`.\n\nUses `task_id` captured from a previous `POST /tasks` response."
					},
					"response": []
				}
